column5: For anyone that lives up in that area or fishes it I am wondering if someone knows of any private boat launches on Storm or Route Bay that could be used? Thanks, Fred
Smith's Camp on Storm Bay Rd. has a launch. I think it's $15.00.
There is a small marina/launch in route bay but I don't know their names or if they accept short term launch.
Thanks Deadhead1 I will do a little searching and see if I can find it. Fred
